#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kdf.appdata.xml:10
msgid "View Disk Usage"
msgstr "Kettakasutuse näitamine"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kdf.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KDiskFree displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, floppy "
"and CD drives, etc.) along with information on their capacity, free space, "
"type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and unmount drives and "
"view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"KDiskFree näitab saadaolevaid failiseadmeid (kõvaketta partitsioonid, "
"disketid, CD-d jne) ühes teabega nende mahu, vaba ruumi, tüübi ja "
"haakepunkti kohta. Samuti saab selle abil kettaid ühendada ja lahutada ning "
"näha neid failihalduris."

